div1.p: I JH McGraw, Sheriff of King County W.T. do hereby certify that I received a writ, of which the within is a full true and correct copy, on the 27th day of May, 1885, and that I personally served the same on the same day on, James H. Woolery, Chief of Police of the City of Seattle, by delivering said writ to him the said Chief of Police, personally, in King County W.T.
Dated at Seattle the 28" day of May 1885, JH McGraw Sheriff
Sheriff's Fees Service 1.00 Copy of Writ .40 Travel 20 Certificate 50 $2.10
No 4437. District Court 3rd Judicial District City of Seattle vs. Lee Kee Writ of Habeas Corpus
